cs.MA, cs.LO, cs.PL, cs.SY, cs.RO 

Reasoning: 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is the most likely category as the paper deals with a team of agents and their control and communication strategies. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is also likely as the paper uses Linear Temporal Logic (LTL) to specify the global task and generate individual control strategies. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is relevant as the paper proposes a computational framework for generating control and communication strategies. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with the synthesis of control and communication strategies for a team of agents. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is relevant as the paper applies the proposed method to deploy a team of miniature cars in a robotic environment.
